ΑΙΧΑΔΩΙΙΛΝLΧ

Apparatus criticus

Text of Gualtherus 1624 [1625], reproduced by Crispi; Gualtherus 1624 (after Cordici?) transcribed: ΩΙΧΛΔΟLIILIXL

translation

commentary

There is some uncertainty among earlier authors whether the text is even ancient Greek, although on balance of probability it would seem to be so.
